Subject: [PATCH 05/18] fix(P2b): replace hardcoded rgba/hex with derived
 design tokens
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Dashboard.tsx: 2 chart tooltips #131722 → var(--color-card), border rgba → var(--color-border-medium)
- Dashboard.tsx: backtest button color '#fff' → var(--color-text-primary)
- PreMatch.tsx: active tab text '#000' → var(--color-on-accent)
- PreMatch.tsx: skeleton gradient #1e293b/#334155 → var(--color-bg-secondary)/var(--color-card-hover)
- PreMatch.tsx: error banner bg rgba(255,23,68,0.1) → var(--color-danger-bg-soft), border → var(--color-danger)
- MMAPreMatch.tsx: warning bg rgba(148,163,184,0.08) → var(--color-border-medium)
- MMAPreMatch.tsx: divider line rgba(255,255,255,0.15) → var(--color-divider)
- H2HPage.tsx: progress bar bg rgba(255,255,255,0.08) → var(--color-border-medium)
- PlayerProfileModal.tsx: overlay rgba(0,0,0,0.7) → var(--color-overlay)

Note: PreMatch.tsx inline code blocks (rgba(0,0,0,0.3)) kept as-is per audit fallback guidance.
Note: MatchesTab.tsx live/error border glows (rgba 0.3) kept as-is for visual effect.
